Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gala Puska開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,敵方艦隊51%沉默或消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,成了 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,掃蕩敵人的殘余兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,跟緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了渡瀨青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,佐及利亞…萬歲
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:45.70,T,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,500)\pos(1500,885.333)}{\blur4}{\pos(528,479.333)}接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,打擊部隊突破敵方前線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gala Puska準備開第二砲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,第二砲？作戰方案中應該沒有註明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,司令官是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,敵軍衝入我方前線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,讓殘余兵力集中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,兵力上應該還是我方占優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓那門炮再開火了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,艦隊旗艦命令遊擊部隊摧毀Gorgon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是要我們在這種情況下衝進敵方基地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,您作何決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,命令終歸是命令 只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,明白 全速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你們將決定這場戰役的勝敗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 迪奧 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不過絕對別用現在的機體來配對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆的調整數據我會預先發送的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,機體雖不一樣駕駛艙是一樣的 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,跟緊我 別落後了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:01:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,居然想開第二炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,說預計在15分鐘後開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢材 被橫貫秋空的戰果衝昏頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可是再開一炮毫無疑問能一錘定音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,難道以為足以摧毀城市消滅艦隊的武器 可以無限制地開火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gala Puska的能量來源就是Nectoribium本身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,用它開一砲要消耗的Nectoribium 相當於我佐及利亞一整年的採掘量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一整年的量？怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了戰役毀了國家是毫無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是促使司令使用這武器的人是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾弗雷德·加倫特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,中校？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,乘敵軍混亂我們一舉拿下勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,佐及利亞…萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我艦被捲了入與佐及利亞軍先頭部隊的交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就沒工夫管Gorgon了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Valiancer隊出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一下子就要進激戰區嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,別廢話了 雅爾 出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 推不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,敵軍一下子變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,打開一個突破口 跟緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒必要了 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,貝宗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟雛會消滅敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雛 來 配對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,全程序準備就緒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,連接雛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 雛 不是該說接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真會幫我多事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fs34}{\fad(100,0)} Force Coupling-強制配對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我好像有失誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,障礙已經解除了 已經沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我當心 要是我的雛有個三長兩短怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,來了 連接雛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,來 讓他們見識見識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,佐及利亞…萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Indefatigable、Inflexible的Valiancer隊潰滅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,確認敵方Valiancer兩機的識別碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是配對機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到對方也有配對者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈 看啊 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們倆的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,貝宗…他是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,別錯過機會了 上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是白鳥啊 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉自己送上門來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,礙事了 滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能打得過配對機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 Cygnus要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,左翼Nectar炮中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,右翼引擎艙中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,輸出功率降低40%
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,距離Nectar屏障下一發填充還有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧！！嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,熱能探測
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是Luxon Next和Bradyon Next
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哈呀 總算來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是Nectar步槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是無核對數據的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,新型機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,配對了 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,別命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,連接迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄登場了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一點沒說錯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//CM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是配對機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是聯合軍的新型配對機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在上面的大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是渡瀨青葉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那台Valiancer…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是你在過去見過的那台嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 來殺我的那台和雛開來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,上了 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是雛坐在上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那新型機是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是配對機之間的戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Emphatier Level 90%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是到現在最高的契合度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼快就要親眼看到配對機之間的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看來能收集到寶貴的數據了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,艾爾薇拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你來看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,總之這樣一來敵方的壓倒性優勢是蕩然無存了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 盡全力攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是決勝的關鍵時刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,部隊出現損失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,失去發動奇襲的優勢了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到我們也陷入了將戰局交由配對機決定的境地了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 好強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉 不做擊落敵機的打算你自己就會被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,發現了奇怪的噪音就試著解析了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,敵方的配對似乎有所勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是用什麼方式強制實施的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒錯就有機可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,於是我有一個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這是賭博 而且局勢相當不樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我試試 雛一定坐在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,來了 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,解除配對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,解除配對了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雛 聽得到嗎 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 可惡 駕駛艙裡居然沒有這樣的功能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雛 我是青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,青…葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊 渡瀨青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雛就是雛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…青葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:09:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,雛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,強制解除配對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 你做了什麼青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,迪奧 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gorgon好像開始填充第二砲的能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,預計4分鐘後開砲 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,衝過去 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,距離發射還有3分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,請您等一下 戰場上還有友軍部隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,都已經預先通知了 照原定計劃開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,三台Valiancer正急速靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,清醒了嗎 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到雛居然是配對者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該拒絕了哈恩博士的搭乘請求的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,具體我也不清楚但想必他是不擇手段了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的雛給…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雛 你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再配對一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 貝宗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他們要來了 抓緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fs34}{\fad(100,0)} Force Coupling ready
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,連接雛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 雛 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,回應我 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,雛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,敵機正發起強制配對請求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哈恩 你將無視配對者意志的配對化為可能了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,受縛於既成概念才是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去敵人會實現強制配對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,雛 現在你跟我來配對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 雛 要相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,噢…雛 連接 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,動手 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,連接 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Emphatier Level上升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還在持續上升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,梁贊少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛開始其實恨過你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但你一直都肯相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這次輪到我來相信你了 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…為什麼 雛 這是為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了？那個光點是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 Gala Puska開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,坐標(125,-979)出現成因不明的特異點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,開始擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,出現重力異常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,內部水準呈級數增長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,避開 快避開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,原型Valiancer2號機發生推進力異常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,以現在的加速度會被吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,2號機怎麼了 快加速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…呃啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,貝宗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得那個是那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我不是說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,鑽進那個我才來到了現代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,時空隧道？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,時空隧道！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那就是你所說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 的確是那樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡…絕不能饒恕你 渡瀨青葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是因為你帶我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在學校我突然遭到Valiancer的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候不是你救了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉會遭到襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,時空…隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,雛 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉 正如你所說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這次輪到我來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,慢著 雛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 青葉 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,閃開 迪奧 我現在不追上去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,雛！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…給我加速啊 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再見囉 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雛！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊 還有時間的…一定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,等著我 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 雛她 只有雛她一個人活在同一個時間段裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,並將我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雛 她一直重複做著相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我總是沒能阻止雛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雛！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉 正如你所說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這次輪到我來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,慢著 雛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你…不阻止我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我為什麼要阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是雛嗎？那個救了你性命的雛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對啊 你已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再見囉 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,雛 不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再重複循環了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是不去貝宗可是會去殺了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在對他說什麼都是沒用的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了 青葉 別射偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在幹什麼 你們這群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡啊…青葉 雛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退！撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,貝宗他怎麼樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拉斯加基地被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,戰爭還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這是給予經不起Nectoribium誘惑的人的懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,佐及利亞軍開始撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好歹是活下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是迪奧 馬上會合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,同樣是青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄們返航了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉 你為什麼阻止了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你問我為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是不想讓雛你再回到過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你回到過去的機會嗎 你為什麼不掌握…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他是個做事不經大腦的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼！？說不定還有機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好樂觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因為俗話不是這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,未來會發生什麼誰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,青葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我一不在就會有人寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你在說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還有誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你反應出乎意料的遲鈍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}還…還輪不到你來說我 說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 誰都不清楚未來會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bradyon Next、Luxon Next外加擄獲的敵機一台馬上回艦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Valiancer隊回艦準備就緒
